msgid "DecentralChain is a cutting-edge, secure and efficient blockchainecosystem empowering smart contract creation, decentralized application(DApps) development and a thriving decentralized finance (DeFi)community. It utilizes a consensus protocol called Leased Proof of Stake(LPoS) which aims to improve upon traditional Proof of Stake (PoS) byallowing users to lease their stakes to other users, which increases thelatter's ability to produce new blocks. In return, the lender receives apercentage of the transaction fees earned by the validator. This leasingmechanism aims to address the possible centralization problem intraditional PoS models where a few large stakeholders control asignificant portion of the network, and the decision-making power isconcentrated in the hands of a small group of individuals or entitieswhile at the same time allowing all users to earn rewards, extending theability to participate in the network to not only minority stakeholdersbut also users who just want to lease their stakes to other users."
