#: ../../01_introduction.md:94
msgid "DecentralChain offers a unique approach to decentralized applicationdevelopment by avoiding high gas fees for all transactions. Theblockchain's native language, called Ride, is a non-Turing-completelanguage, which helps keep the system secure and predictable. Ride allows for the creation of smart contracts, which are self-executing agreements written in code that run without a central entity behind them. Thisprovides a platform for decentralized applications (DApps), which areapplications that work without a central authority. DecentralChain's useof Ride and LPoS helps to ensure the stability and security of thenetwork, making it an attractive option for decentralized applicationdevelopment."
